### Frequent Clients API

### List frequent clients (Staff/Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/frequent-clients
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create frequent client (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/frequent-clients
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "VIP Client",
  "phone": "+19569990000",
  "defaultTableIds": ["A27", "A28"],
  "tableSettings": [
    {
      "tableId": "A27",
      "paymentStatus": "PENDING",
      "amountDue": 100,
      "amountPaid": 0,
      "paymentDeadlineTime": "00:00",
      "paymentDeadlineTz": "America/Chicago"
    }
  ],
  "notes": "Prefers front section"
}

###

### Get frequent client by id
@frequentClientId = REPLACE_FREQUENT_CLIENT_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/frequent-clients/{{frequentClientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update frequent client (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/frequent-clients/{{frequentClientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "defaultTableIds": ["A27"],
  "tableSettings": [
    {
      "tableId": "A27",
      "paymentStatus": "COURTESY",
      "amountDue": 0,
      "amountPaid": 0,
      "paymentDeadlineTime": "00:00",
      "paymentDeadlineTz": "America/Chicago"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Delete frequent client (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/frequent-clients/{{frequentClientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
